WEBVTT

00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:02.440
I've been doing some thinking.

00:00:04.240 --> 00:00:06.000
I'm going to kill my dad.

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:08.416
I called my sister.

00:00:08.440 --> 00:00:09.936
"Listen,

00:00:09.960 --> 00:00:11.520
I've been doing some thinking.

00:00:12.480 --> 00:00:14.320
I'm going to kill Dad.

00:00:15.480 --> 00:00:17.120
I'm going to take him to Oregon,

00:00:18.080 --> 00:00:19.976
find some heroin,

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:21.240
and give it to him."

00:00:22.720 --> 00:00:24.856
My dad has frontotemporal lobe dementia,

00:00:24.880 --> 00:00:26.616
or FTD.

00:00:26.640 --> 00:00:29.576
It's a confusing disease
that hits people in their 50s or 60s.

00:00:29.600 --> 00:00:32.496
It can completely change
someone's personality,